2

  • Class Name: android.widget.ImageButton

  • View ID: com.eterno:id/notification_image

Alternative Text

Critical

Images and media elements must have an alternative text that describes their content and can be read and announced by assistive technologies. However, If the image is solely for decorative purposes and not essential or supporting the content, it should be hidden from assistive technologies.
  • 1.1.1 Non-text Content (A)

Color Contrast

Serious

Ensures the contrast between foreground and background colors meets WCAG 2 AA contrast ratio thresholds. The minimum contrast ratio is 4.5:1 for font sizes less than 24dp and 3:1 for font sizes 24dp or higher.

Background #ffffff

4.50 suggested ratio
